					<description><![CDATA[<p>Binance Wallet has announced a new trading competition for Irys (IRYS) on the Binance Alpha platform. The Binance Alpha IRYS trading competition will run from June 4 to June 11,</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-irys-trading-competition-guide/" data-wpel-link="internal">Join the Binance Alpha IRYS Trading Competition, Trade and Share in $100K Rewards</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><a href="https://tk-ventures.slack.com/archives/D0B4FNN8S2E/p1779815666453879" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external">Binance</a> Wallet has </span><a href="https://www.binance.com/en/support/announcement/detail/e03b8b6a88284e579613a37542b5eb7c?utm_source=EnglishTelegram&amp;utm_medium=GlobalCommunity&amp;utm_campaign=AnnouncementBot" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><span style="font-weight: 400;">announced</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> a new trading competition for Irys (IRYS) on the Binance Alpha platform. The Binance Alpha IRYS trading competition will run from June 4 to June 11, giving traders the chance to compete for a share of $100,000 in rewards.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Binance users who trade $IRYS on the Binance Wallet (Keyless) or Binance Alpha will qualify to share in the rewards. Traders who trade IRYS on the first and second day will get a 3x multiplier on all their cumulative IRYS buy positions. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This guide contains everything you need to know about the Binance Alpha IRYS Trading Competition. If you do not want to trade an alpha token, you can sign up with our Binance Referral Code: O0BTS35, and you’ll earn $100 in USDT and an extra 10% trading fee rebates.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: 400;"><div class="b-cta-wrapper"><div class="b-cta b-cta--inline"><div class="b-cta__meta"><div class="user-score"></div><div class="promotion"></div></div><div class="b-cta__btn d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"></div></div><!-- /.b-cta --></div></span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">About IRYS</span></h2>
<div id="attachment_202500" style="width: 1610px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-202500" class="size-full wp-image-202500" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/unnamed-38.jpg" alt="About IRYS" width="1600" height="700" /><p id="caption-attachment-202500" class="wp-caption-text">Source: IRYS</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">IRYS is a revolutionary provenance layer designed for Web3 data infrastructure. It ensures data is permanently and securely stored with clear tracking. Irys specializes in managing massive data volumes with absolute cryptographic precision. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">IRYS serves as the native utility token within this growing ecosystem to facilitate node staking, data storage payments, and decentralized governance. This Alpha new trading competition marks an important milestone in driving global adoption for the Irys network.</span></p>
<p><b><i>More Binance Events: </i></b><a href="https://chainplay.gg/blog/binance-strax-trading-tournament-guide/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><b><i>Join the Binance STRAX Trading Tournament Guide</i></b></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Details of the Binance IRYS Trading Competition</span></h2>
<div id="attachment_202499" style="width: 1610px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-202499" class="size-full wp-image-202499" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/unnamed-39.jpg" alt="Binance IRYS Trading Competition" width="1600" height="900" /><p id="caption-attachment-202499" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Binance</p></div>
<ul>
<li><b>Reward Pool:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 4,760,000 IRYS tokens</span></li>
<li><b>Reward Distribution: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">2,380 IRYS Per User</span></li>
<li><b>Eligible Trading Pairs: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">IRYS Purchase on Binance Alpha</span></li>
<li><b>Contest Duration:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> June 4, 2026, to June 11, 2026, 13:00 (UTC)</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Eligible trades will be ranked based on your total purchase volume on IRYS during the Promotion Period. Sells and trades won’t count. Traders who make the top 2,000 by trade volume will earn 2,380 $IRYS tokens. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This competition also has a unique early bird multiplier system for early traders. For those who trade on the first four days, their effective trading volume will be multiplied by 3x. The breakdown of the multiplier throughout the IRYS trading competition is:</span></p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><b>Trading Day</b></td>
<td><b>Multiplier</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 1</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 2</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 3</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 4</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">3.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 5</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.0x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 6</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.5x</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Day 7</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">1.0x</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your ranking will be on </span><b>Daily Effective Trading Volume = Actual Trading Volume * Early Bird Boost Multiplier</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">. This means that IRYS buys on June 4 to June 8 of $10,000 will count as $30,000 in effective trading volume. The same $10,000 IRYS purchase on June 11 will count as $10,000. </span></p>
<p><b><i>More Airdrops: </i></b><a href="https://chainplay.gg/blog/binance-opg-trading-tournament-guide/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><b><i>Join the Binance OpenGradient Trading Tournament Guide</i></b></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> </span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Rising Trader Boost</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The IRYS trading competition will also feature the new </span><b>Rising Trader Boost</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> system. This boost applies to anyone who has won rewards in less than five previous Binance Wallet Alpha trading competitions.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Rising Traders will receive a 2x boost on their calculated trading volume. The cap limits the maximum actual volume to $5,000. If you qualify for both boosts, you get an even bigger boost to your trading volume. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your effective daily volume equals your actual volume multiplied by the Early Bird rate, plus your capped volume multiplied by the Rising Trader rate.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">With the same example, the Early Bird Boost of $10,000 on Day 1 = $30,000. Your Rising Trader Boost of $10,000 (only $5,000 qualifies). This means that the Rising Trader Boost = $5,000 * 2 = $10,000. Your Effective Trading Volume will be $20,000 + $10,000 = $30,000.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">How To Participate in the $IRYS Trading Competition</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">To participate in the $IRYS trading competition, do the following.</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Join the Event:</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Open your Binance App, navigate to the event page, and click the </span><b>Join Now</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> button. Only trades made after clicking Join will count.<img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-202498" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/unnamed-40.jpg" alt="$IRYS Trading Competition" width="420" height="243" /></span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Prepare Your Wallet: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ensure you have created and backed up a Binance Wallet (Keyless).</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><b>Purchase IRYS: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Execute buy orders for IRYS via the Binance Wallet or Binance Alpha. Note that only cumulative purchases count; selling volume is excluded.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><b><i>More Binance Events: </i></b><a href="https://chainplay.gg/blog/binance-zest-trading-competition-guide/https:/chainplay.gg/blog/binance-alpha-citrea-airdrop-guide/" data-wpel-link="external" rel="external noopener noreferrer"><b><i>Join the ZEST Trading Competition on Binance Alpha</i></b></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Important Rules for the IRYS Trading Competition</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are participating in the IRYS trading competition, it’s best to understand the rules to know what kind of trades qualify:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Eligible Platforms: Only trades via Binance Wallet (Keyless) or Binance Alpha qualify. Third-party dApps and token bridging are excluded.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Only cumulative IRYS buy trades will count. </span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Token bridging transactions are not eligible for this Promotion.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">There is no maximum limit on how much you can trade.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">You have to claim your tokens within 14 days of them becoming available, or they will be forfeited.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Binance can disqualify any accounts involved in wash trading, bulk registrations, or market manipulation. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you rank in the top 2,000 traders, you will receive 2,380 IRYS tokens at the end of the trading contest. You have 14 days to claim the rewards, or Binance will consider that you forfeit the rewards. Once rewards are marked as claimable, they do not remain in your dashboard indefinitely.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/binance-irys-trading-competition-guide/" data-wpel-link="internal">Join the Binance Alpha IRYS Trading Competition, Trade and Share in $100K Rewards</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
